title: How to deal with missing navigation software data? How to deal with missing authorization documents or activation codes?
answer:
1If you are using the online map, make sure that mobile data or Wi-Fi is enabled. 

2If you are using offline maps, please confirm whether the offline map pack is lost. You can re-download the offline maps or enable the mobile data or Wi-Fi to use the online map. 

 The pre-set navigation software in the phone has no authorization file activation code.
